Once we copy the scripts to bastion, run the following scripts

On source ASG
- ./copy_scripts.sh <src-asg-name>
- ./create_attach_ebs.sh <src-asg-name> <vol-size-in-gb>
- ./list_ebs.sh <src-asg-name>
- ./detach_ebs.sh <src-asg-name>
- ./delete_ebs.sh <src-asg-name> (final step)

On destination ASG
- ./copy_scripts.sh <dest-asg-name>
- ./attach_ebs_ro.sh <dest-asg-name> <src-asg-name>
